text: Agdistis insidiatrix is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from Yemen (Socotra) and Iran.A new species, a new synonym, and new distribution records in the genus Agdistis Hübner, 1825 from Iran (Pterophoridae: Agdistinae) ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Fauna of Socotra Category:Moths described in 1933
title: Agdistis insidiatrix
